Joe BARONI, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6091. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Nov. 3, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

*1019PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for appellee, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
